msgid "Co-created with you"
msgstr "Cocreat amb la vostra participació"

msgctxt "body.4357fc42-1799-427f-b6e8-f9ef89660c4b.left_column.1d2526c5-15dd-4f51-aaf8-541edf138362"
msgid "Most festivals hand you a program. We build ours with community."
msgstr "La majoria dels festivals us faciliten un programa. Nosaltres el construïm amb la comunitat."

msgctxt "body.4357fc42-1799-427f-b6e8-f9ef89660c4b.left_column.1d2526c5-15dd-4f51-aaf8-541edf138362"
msgid "People from around the world propose the sessions, host the conversations, and shape what MozFest becomes each year."
msgstr "Persones de tot el món proposen les sessions, organitzen debats i donen forma al MozFest de cada any."

msgctxt "body.4357fc42-1799-427f-b6e8-f9ef89660c4b.left_column.1d2526c5-15dd-4f51-aaf8-541edf138362"
msgid "That means the program stays close to what's actually happening on the ground—what you're working on, worried about, and ready to change."
msgstr "Això significa que el programa es manté proper al que realment passa sobre el terreny: allò en què esteu treballant, allò que us preocupa i allò que esteu disposats a canviar."

msgctxt "body.4357fc42-1799-427f-b6e8-f9ef89660c4b.left_column.1d2526c5-15dd-4f51-aaf8-541edf138362"
msgid "You don't just attend. We co-build together."
msgstr "No només hi assistiu. Ho coconstruïm junts."

