msgctxt "body.1d261775-1bd1-4c94-a2ee-4fd0698decd1"
msgid "2025 Festival Highlights"
msgstr "Moments destacats del Festival del 2025"

msgctxt "body.1d261775-1bd1-4c94-a2ee-4fd0698decd1"
msgid "Revisit 2025’s Great Unlearning"
msgstr "Recordem el Great Unlearning del 2025"

msgctxt "body.1d261775-1bd1-4c94-a2ee-4fd0698decd1"
msgid "In 2025, more than 2000 people came together In Barcelona to unlearn the old rules of the internet—and imagine new ways to build, connect, and create together."
msgstr "El 2025, més de 2.000 persones es van reunir a Barcelona per desaprendre les velles normes d'internet i pensar noves maneres de construir, connectar i crear junts."

msgctxt "body.1d261775-1bd1-4c94-a2ee-4fd0698decd1"
msgid ""
"Mainstage moments included Ruha Benjamin exploring how power operates through the stories we inherit and how breaking free from them can unlock new ways of thinking and building, and Chelsea Manning"
" sharing her 'world of new learnings'—both a cautionary tale and a call to action."
msgstr ""
"Per l'escenari principal van passar Ruha Benjamin, que va parlar sobre com el poder opera a través de les històries que heretem i com podem descobrir noves maneres de pensar i construir si ens "
"n'alliberem, i Chelsea Manning, que va compartir el seu \"món de nous aprenentatges\", a tall d'advertència i de crida a l'acció, entre altres ponents."

msgctxt "body.1d261775-1bd1-4c94-a2ee-4fd0698decd1"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\">Watch the highlights</a>"
msgstr "<a id=\"a1\">Mira els moments destacats</a>"

msgctxt "body.79c80884-883e-4948-aad0-f0c99858f80c.left_column.3ddc6f87-677a-485e-b4ae-45b28da8fa07.title"
msgid "2,000 people. One shared direction."
msgstr "2.000 persones. Una mateixa direcció."

msgctxt "body.79c80884-883e-4948-aad0-f0c99858f80c.left_column.3ddc6f87-677a-485e-b4ae-45b28da8fa07.image.alt_text"
